title: Automatic 8 cylinders injector tester and cleaner US-SD5
title_uz: Avtomatik 8 silindrli injektor tozalash uskunasi US-SD5
title_ru: Автоматический тестер и очиститель форсунок 8 цилиндров US-SD5
title_en: Automatic 8 cylinders injector tester and cleaner US-SD5
short_description: The US-SD5 model 8-cylinder injector cleaning equipment has a multi-function system, which includes: direct spraying, back spraying, ultrasonic cleaning, automatic cleaning functions. In addition, the equipment has the ability to test 8 injectors at the same time. It is also possible to check injector fuel distribution and delivery. Also, the equipment has a multilingual control panel, which allows control in English, Russian, Arabic, Spanish and other languages. The control system with LED display on the equipment provides a clear menu and easy operation. In addition, the equipment automatically returns the liquid in the pipe to the tank.
short_description_uz: US-SD5 modeldagi 8 silindrli injektor tozalash uskunasida ko’p funksiyaviylik tizimi mavjud bo'lib, ular: to’g’ridan-to`g`ri purkash, ortga purkash, ultratovushli tozalash, avtomatik tozalash funksiyalari hisoblanadi. Bundan tashqari, uskunada 8 ta injektorni bir vaqtning o'zida sinab ko'rish imkoniyati mavjud. Shuningdek, injektor yoqilg'isini taqsimlash va yetkazib berishni tekshirish mumkin. Yana, uskunada ko’p tilli boshqaruv paneli mavjud bo'lib, bu ingliz, rus, arab, ispan va boshqa tillarda boshqarish imkoniyatini beradi. Uskunadagi LED displeyli boshqaruv tizimi esa aniq menyu va oson ishlash imkoniyatini beradi. Bularga qo'shimcha ravishda, uskunada quvurdagi suyuqlik avtomatik ravishda tankga qaytariladi.
short_description_ru: Оборудование для очистки 8-цилиндровых форсунок модели US-SD5 имеет многофункциональную систему, которая включает в себя: прямое распыление, обратное распыление, ультразвуковую очистку, функции автоматической очистки. Кроме того, оборудование имеет возможность проверки 8 форсунок одновременно. Также можно проверить распределение и подачу топлива через форсунку. Также оборудование имеет мультиязычную панель управления, позволяющую управлять на английском, русском, арабском, испанском и других языках. Система управления со светодиодным дисплеем на оборудовании обеспечивает понятное меню и простоту эксплуатации. Кроме того, оборудование автоматически возвращает жидкость в трубе в бак.
short_description_en: The US-SD5 model 8-cylinder injector cleaning equipment has a multi-function system, which includes: direct spraying, back spraying, ultrasonic cleaning, automatic cleaning functions. In addition, the equipment has the ability to test 8 injectors at the same time. It is also possible to check injector fuel distribution and delivery. Also, the equipment has a multilingual control panel, which allows control in English, Russian, Arabic, Spanish and other languages. The control system with LED display on the equipment provides a clear menu and easy operation. In addition, the equipment automatically returns the liquid in the pipe to the tank.
long_description:
Automatic 8 cylinders injector tester and cleaner US-SD5.

Technical indicators of the equipment:

  • Model: US-SD5.
  • Power supply: AC 220 V / 110 V±10%, 50-60 Hz.
  • Input power: 250 W.
  • Simulated RPM range/step: 10000 rpm / 50 rpm.
  • Injection time: 0-600 sec, step 1 sec.
  • Test liquid tank volume:  6 L.
  • Suction speed: 6.5 L/min.
  • Cylinder size: 10 L.
  • Testing tube volume: 120 ml.
  • Dimensions: 62 x 53 x 74 cm.
  • Weight: 54 kg.
  • Country of manufacture: China.
